            "style": "",
            "text": " is adding some new color options that will probably appeal to vintage racing enthusiasts. After posting a teaser video on social media, Chevrolet has confirmed changes to the C8 Corvettes sophomore year, which is mostly limited to a broader color palette and added content.",
